oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Jerry Clower and Mel Street at Macon Coliseum (17849)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Clower, Jerry, 1926-1998; Street, Mel; Spears, Billie Jo; Hitchcock, Stan; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and black on white) announcing Grand Ole Opry stars Jerry Clower, Mel Street, Billie Joe Spears, and Stan Hitchcock at the Macon Coliseum on August 11. Poster features metal photoplates of Jerry Clower, Mel Street, Billie Joe Spears, and Stan Hitchcock. For additional information about this poster see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/22475.
